						               													<description>From the Publisher:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Learning has never been this much fun! Wordplay For Kids allows children to develop many vital skills while playing a truly unique game. All children participate in every round, with a whole new challenge arising every time. The idea is wonderfully simple: children try to form a word that contains certain letters, which they acquire by using the letter spinner. The longer the word, the more points are given. Six special categories guide the kids along - &amp;quot;Food or Drink&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Object or Thing&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Living Creature&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Something in the House&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Boy's or Girl's Name&amp;quot; and &amp;quot;Any Word&amp;quot;. To add to the excitement, the word must be formed before time runs out! Wordplay For Kids is not only challenging and competitive to play, but it is also a way for children to constantly test and improve world building skills in a fun environment.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
